      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COMPTON TIG (2) was chasing the leaders from a low draw and kept coming to score (23.61) at this track in Other over 400m. Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Looks the one to beat. LADY BOMBSHELL (5) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (18.47) last time in a Other at this track. Form here sound including five wins. Comes through a solid form race last start. Should be about the money. JAJA DING DONG (7) showed little early speed at her last couple, the latest finishing fourth (23.98) in a Other at this track. Must be included in calculations. SASSY LAD (8) will make his presence felt following a brief layoff.",
